fields.excerpt_html:
This blog describes the journey that I, a developer took to decide the
architecture to use for the implementation of a recent project I have been
working on. It demonstrates the thought process a developer goes through to
come to a resolution.

frontmatter.title: The Development Journey for Choosing an Architecture

fields.excerpt_html:
Learn the differences between different string literals in Python and how
escape characters work differently between them. Also understand the encoding
and decoding functionality with Python strings.
Learn how to generate excerpts with gatsby-transformer-remark and work around the lack of the excerpt_separator option in gatsby-plugin-mdx.

frontmatter.title: Generating excerpts using GatsbyJS Markdown plugins
